    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Python学习"><a href="#Python学习" class="headerlink" title="Python学习"></a>Python学习</h1><h3 id="0：格式格式-对齐对齐"><a href="#0：格式格式-对齐对齐" class="headerlink" title="!!!0：格式格式!!!对齐对齐!!!"></a>!!!0：格式格式!!!对齐对齐!!!</h3><h3 id="自定义封装函数："><a href="#自定义封装函数：" class="headerlink" title="自定义封装函数："></a>自定义封装函数：</h3><blockquote><p>函数框架：</p><p>  def 函数名（参数）：</p><p>​         函数体</p><p>​         return 语句</p></blockquote><h4 id="问题1："><a href="#问题1：" class="headerlink" title="问题1："></a>问题1：</h4><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">hanshu</span>(<span class="params">x</span>):</span><br><span class="line">    x = <span class="number">2</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">print</span>(x)</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">8</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>无输出。</p><h5 id="问题1解决"><a href="#问题1解决" class="headerlink" title="问题1解决"></a><strong>问题1解决</strong></h5><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">hanshu</span>(<span class="params">x</span>):</span><br><span class="line">    x = <span class="number">2</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">print</span>(x)</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">8</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(hanshu(<span class="number">6</span>))</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="原因：没有调用函数（）。"><a href="#原因：没有调用函数（）。" class="headerlink" title="原因：没有调用函数（）。"></a><strong>原因</strong>：没有调用函数（）。</h5><h4 id="问题2：位置参数，默认参数，元组，可变参数"><a href="#问题2：位置参数，默认参数，元组，可变参数" class="headerlink" title="问题2：位置参数，默认参数，元组，可变参数"></a>问题2：位置参数，默认参数，元组，可变参数</h4><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">tianqi</span>(<span class="params">tianqinie</span>):</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;今天天气是：&#x27;</span>+tianqinie+<span class="string">&#x27;\n&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">tianqi(<span class="string">&#x27;晴天&#x27;</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">menu</span>(<span class="params">staters,staple_food,dessert=<span class="string">&#x27;布丁&#x27;</span></span>):</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;这个顾客点的开胃菜是&#x27;</span>+staters+<span class="string">&#x27;,主食是&#x27;</span>+staple_food+<span class="string">&#x27;,甜品是&#x27;</span>+dessert+<span class="string">&#x27;。\n&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">menu(<span class="string">&#x27;酸辣白菜&#x27;</span>,<span class="string">&#x27;米饭&#x27;</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">menu</span>(<span class="params">*dessert</span>):</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> i <span class="keyword">in</span> dessert:</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;今日新推出的甜点有：&#x27;</span>+i)</span><br><span class="line">menu(<span class="string">&#x27;布丁&#x27;</span>,<span class="string">&#x27;酸奶&#x27;</span>,<span class="string">&#x27;面包&#x27;</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">menu</span>(<span class="params">greens, staple_food, *barbecue, dessert=<span class="string">&#x27;布丁&#x27;</span></span>):</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;38号桌顾客点的热菜：&#x27;</span> + greens + <span class="string">&#x27;\n主食：&#x27;</span> + staple_food)</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> i <span class="keyword">in</span> barbecue:</span><br><span class="line">         <span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;烧烤:&#x27;</span> + i)</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;甜点:&#x27;</span> + dessert)</span><br><span class="line">menu(<span class="string">&#x27;红烧带鱼&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;米饭&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;羊肉串&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;烤肥肠&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;烤茄子&#x27;</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="问题3："><a href="#问题3：" class="headerlink" title="问题3："></a>问题3：</h4><p>global：调用全局变量</p><h3 id="类："><a href="#类：" class="headerlink" title="类："></a>类：</h3><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">Person</span>(<span class="title class_ inherited__">object</span>):  <span class="comment"># 定义一个父类</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">talk</span>(<span class="params">self</span>):  <span class="comment"># 父类中的方法</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">&quot;person is talking....&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">Chinese</span>(<span class="title class_ inherited__">Person</span>):  <span class="comment"># 定义一个子类， 继承Person类</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">walk</span>(<span class="params">self</span>):  <span class="comment"># 在子类中定义其自身的方法</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;is walking...&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">c = Chinese()</span><br><span class="line">c.talk()  <span class="comment"># 调用继承的Person类的方法</span></span><br><span class="line">c.walk()  <span class="comment"># 调用本身的方法</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="文件操作："><a href="#文件操作：" class="headerlink" title="文件操作："></a>文件操作：</h3><h4 id="open："><a href="#open：" class="headerlink" title="open："></a>open：</h4><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">open</span>(文件名,打开方式,encoding=<span class="string">&#x27;编码方式&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">with</span> <span class="built_in">open</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;sbc.txt&#x27;</span>,<span class="string">&#x27;a&#x27;</span>) <span class="keyword">as</span> filel:</span><br><span class="line">file.read():</span><br><span class="line">file.readinglines():</span><br><span class="line">filel = <span class="built_in">open</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;abc.txt&#x27;</span>,<span class="string">&#x27;w&#x27;</span>,encoding=<span class="string">&#x27;utf-8&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">filel.write(<span class="string">&#x27;tiantian&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">filel.close()</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="常见报错："><a href="#常见报错：" class="headerlink" title="常见报错："></a>常见报错：</h3><p>。。。。。。。</p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
