    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="异或"><a href="#异或" class="headerlink" title="[异或]^"></a>[异或]^</h1><hr><h3 id="异或：-xor-相同为0，不同为1"><a href="#异或：-xor-相同为0，不同为1" class="headerlink" title="异或：^(xor)  相同为0，不同为1"></a>异或：^(xor)  相同为0，不同为1</h3><h4 id="特点："><a href="#特点：" class="headerlink" title="特点："></a>特点：</h4><p>0^任何数&#x3D;任何数；1^任何数&#x3D;(奇数减一，偶数加一？)</p><hr><h3 id="应用-交换"><a href="#应用-交换" class="headerlink" title="应用 交换"></a>应用 交换</h3><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">int</span> <span class="title">swap</span><span class="params">(<span class="type">int</span> x,<span class="type">int</span> y)</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    x=^y;y=^x;x=^y;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="应用-特定位置位翻转"><a href="#应用-特定位置位翻转" class="headerlink" title="应用 特定位置位翻转"></a>应用 特定位置位翻转</h3><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">与特定位的<span class="number">1</span>取异或</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="应用-查找“单身狗”（判断两个数是否相等）"><a href="#应用-查找“单身狗”（判断两个数是否相等）" class="headerlink" title="应用 查找“单身狗”（判断两个数是否相等）"></a>应用 查找“单身狗”（判断两个数是否相等）</h3><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">//输入数组</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> a[<span class="number">100</span>];</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> k;cin&gt;&gt;k;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="type">int</span> i=<span class="number">0</span>;i&lt;k;i++)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        cin&gt;&gt;a[i];</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">//单个狗2n+1</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> y=<span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="type">int</span> j=<span class="number">0</span>;j&lt;k;j++)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        y=y^*(a+j);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    cout&lt;&lt;y&lt;&lt;endl;</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">//两个狗2n+2</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> z=<span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">while</span>(z%<span class="number">2</span>==<span class="number">0</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        z++;</span><br><span class="line">        y&gt;&gt;<span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> A=<span class="number">0</span> ,B=<span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="type">int</span> p=<span class="number">0</span>;p&lt;k;p++)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span>((*(a+p)&gt;&gt;(z<span class="number">-1</span>))%<span class="number">2</span>==<span class="number">0</span>)A=A^*(a+p);</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">else</span> B=B^*(a+p);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    cout&lt;&lt;A&lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot; &quot;</span>&lt;&lt;B&lt;&lt;endl;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="应用-加密（？（不可逆（"><a href="#应用-加密（？（不可逆（" class="headerlink" title="应用 加密（？（不可逆（"></a>应用 加密（？（不可逆（</h3><h3 id=""><a href="#" class="headerlink" title=""></a></h3>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
